<H3> <TI>   Pepes Leader Denies `Threats' to Escobar's Widow </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  PA2803152894 Santa Fe de Bogota Inravision Television Cadena 
1 in Spanish 1800 GMT 26 Mar 94 </F>

<F P=103> PA2803152894 </F>
<F P=104>  Santa Fe de Bogota Inravision Television Cadena 
1 </F>



<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Spanish </F>
Article Type:BFN 

<F P=106> ["Last-minute report" from the "NTC News" newscast] </F>
  [Text] Maria Victoria Henao, Pablo Escobar's widow, has 
just received a letter signed by Fidel Castano, who is said to 
be the leader of the Pepes [Persecuted by Pablo Escobar]. 
Castano says he is not the author of the threats received by 
the Escobar family in the past days. 

</TEXT>

