<F P=103> PY2903190194 </F>
<F P=104>  La Paz Television Nacional Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Spanish </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Coca producers from Cochabamba's tropical region 
have suspended their peasant and self-defense patrols following 
the signing of an agreement with the government. They will 
maintain alert, however, until the government fulfills its 
promises. The report was provided by coca producers leader Evo 
Morales to Fides News Agency. 
