<H3> <TI>   Workers Destroy Property at Jujuy Government House </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  PY2903175194 Buenos Aires NOTICIAS ARGENTINAS in Spanish 
1600 GMT 29 Mar 94 </F>

<F P=103> PY2903175194 </F>
<F P=104>  Buenos Aires NOTICIAS ARGENTINAS </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Spanish </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] San Salvador de Jujuy, 29 Mar (NA) -- More than 
1,000 Jujuy Province government workers at noon today destroyed 
public property outside the provincial Government House in 
response to Jujuy Government Minister Antonio Paliari's refusal 
to approve a salary increase for the workers. 
  After the incidents, police personnel used tear gas to 
disperse the demonstrators. No major damage or injuries have 
been reported. 

</TEXT>

