<H3> <TI>   Castro Attends CTC National Committee Plenum </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  FL2903232594 Havana Radio Reloj Network in Spanish 2032 GMT 
29 Mar 94 </F>

<F P=103> FL2903232594 </F>
<F P=104>  Havana Radio Reloj Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Spanish </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Commander in Chief Fidel Castro, president of the 
Councils of State and Ministers, is present at the plenum of the 
expanded national committee of the Cuban Workers Federation 
[CTC] being held in Havana. The meeting concludes the first 
phase of the workers parliaments process, which has been carried 
