<H4>   Envoy to Israel Recalled </H4>
<F P=102> NC2602133294 Shanayh Voice of the Mountain in Arabic 1230 
GMT 26 Feb 94 </F>

<F P=103> NC2602133294 </F>
<F P=104>  Shanayh Voice of the Mountain </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Arabic </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] The Egyptian Foreign Ministry has decided to recall 
its ambassador from Israel for consultations following the 
Israeli massacre. Reports say that Egypt, the Palestinians, and 
the Israelis are holding exchanges aiming to find an acceptable 
response to the massacre. 
  Today, a large number of the Israeli diplomatic mission's 
personnel left Cairo as part of the security precautions adopted 
by the Israelis in Egypt for fear of reprisals to the massacre. 

</TEXT>

