<H3> <TI>   Bomb Explodes at Cinema in Kkaytan 28 Feb </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  LD2802114094 Kuwait KUNA in Arabic 1048 GMT 28 Feb 94 </F>
<F P=103> LD2802114094 </F>
<F P=104>  Kuwait KUNA </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Arabic </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Kuwait, 28 Feb -- A security source at the Interior 
Ministry announced here this morning that a bomb has exploded at 
the entrance of Granada cinema in Khaytan area west of the city 
of Kuwait. 
  In a statement received by KUNA the source explained that 
"the explosion resulted in the injury of two people and smashed 
glass in the building" 
  The source pointed out that the competent authorities in the 
Interior Ministry have initiated investigation to learn the 
circumstances that led to the incident. 
  The source appealed to whoever has any information about the 
incident to immediately contact the nearest police station to 
give information to facilitate the task of the security 
apparatus in identifying the perpetrators. 
  The security source, at the end of its statement, expressed 
its indignation at this criminal act, which has targeted the 
lives of the innocent. The source expressed the hope that the 
security services, with the cooperation of the citizens and 
those who were at the cinema, would be able to apprehend the 
perpetrator as quickly as possible. 

</TEXT>

