<H3> <TI>   President Weizman Tours Hebron, Qiryat Arba' </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  TA2702122694 Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el in Hebrew 1200 GMT 27 
Feb 94 </F>

<F P=103> TA2702122694 </F>
<F P=104>  Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Hebrew </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] President 'Ezer Weizman this morning toured Qiryat 
Arba' and met the heads of its council. The president explained 
to them the gravity of the incident in the Cave of Patriarchs, 
and said that it stands in contradiction to every Jewish concept 
as well as the security doctrines as the IDF [Israel Defense 
Forces] teaches them. 
  Earlier, the president toured Hebron. He met the mayor and 
spoke to passersby. The Hebron mayor thanked President Weizman 
for his visit, and asked the Hebron massacre be thoroughly 
investigated, and that conclusions be drawn. 

