<H3> <TI>   Jewish Organization Warns of Retaliation </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  TA2702093794 Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el in Hebrew 0600 GMT 27 
Feb 94 </F>

<F P=103> TA2702093794 </F>
<F P=104>  Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Hebrew </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] An unidentified person telephoned the Qol Yisra'el 
newsroom this morning and said he was speaking on behalf of an 
organization called Shlomtziyon-Yehuda [The Well-Being of 
Zion-Judaea]. He warned that his organization will retaliate to 
every terror attack by Hamas [Islamic Resistance Movement] or 
the Islamic Jihad with murders, in Israel or abroad, which will 
be similar to the Cave of the Patriarchs massacre. The man who 
will carry out the act will never be caught. He will commit 
suicide to sanctify God's name. 

