<H3> <TI>   Husayn Calls al-Hirawi, Denounces Church Incident </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  JN2702162194 Amman Jordan Television Network in Arabic 1500 
GMT 27 Feb 94 </F>

<F P=103> JN2702162194 </F>
<F P=104>  Amman Jordan Television Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Arabic </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] In a telephone conversation with His Excellency 
Lebanese President Ilyas al-Hirawi today, His Majesty King 
Husayn denounced the criminal incident that occurred in Sayyidat 
al-Najat church in Lebanon this morning, killing innocent 
worshipers. 
  On behalf of himself and the people and Government of 
Jordan, 
his majesty offered to his excellency the Lebanese president his 
sincerest condolences for the victims of the outrageous incident. 

</TEXT>

