<F P=100> JORDAN </F>
<H3> <TI>   Paper: Israel Behind Lebanese Church Massacre </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  JN2802105094 Amman SAWT AL-SHA'B in Arabic 28 Feb 94 pp 1, 21 </F>
<F P=103> JN2802105094 </F>
<F P=104>  Amman SAWT AL-SHA'B </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Arabic </F>
Article Type:BFN 

<F P=106> [Editorial: "The Same Party Behind the Two Crimes at the </F>
Ibrahimi Mosque and the Lebanese Church"] 
  [Excerpt] It seems that there is a hostile scheme to drown 
the Arab cordon [al-tawq] states in blood. 
  There is no doubt that Israel and its agents are behind this 
odious scheme. 
  Israel has started to play the tune of sectarianism to sow 
seditions. 
  Israel carried out the Ibrahimi Mosque massacre in Hebron 
and 
also perpetrated another reprehensible crime at the Lebanese 
Sayyidat al-Najat Church. 
  The timing of these two odious crimes is not a coincidence, 
but is the result of a studied and premeditated plan. In view 
of these crimes which have greatly pained the Jordanian leaders 
and people, Jordan, under his Majesty King Husayn, took the 
initiative and acted on all Arab, regional, and international 
levels to acquaint the entire international community of the 
hideousness of this type of terrorism, which undoubtedly is 
Israeli terrorism. [passage omitted] 
  His majesty the king was the first to realize the dimensions 
of this treacherous scheme that is hostile to the cordon states 
and to the peace process which is based on the international 
legitimacy resolutions. His majesty linked the Ibrahimi Mosque 
massacre and the Lebanese Sayyidat al-Najat Church massacre, in 
that there is one party which planned for these two odious 
crimes. 
  His majesty also held consultations with the Lebanese and 
Syrian presidents to contain this odious scheme which seeks to 
drown the region in blood and sow sedition so as to foil it 
before it becomes uncontrollable. [passage omitted] 

</TEXT>

