<H3> <TI>   `Hardline' Groups Vow `Revenge' for Massacre </TI></H3>
<H4>   Islamic Jihad Vows to Revenge Hebron Deaths </H4>
<F P=102> JN2502210794 (Clandestine) Al-Quds Palestinian Arab Radio in 
Arabic 1840 GMT 25 Feb 94 </F>

<F P=103> JN2502210794 </F>
<F P=104>  (Clandestine) Al-Quds Palestinian Arab Radio </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Arabic </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] The Islamic Jihad Movement in Palestine has issued a 
statement in which it said: Our kinsfolk's blood will not go in 
vain. The blood of the faithful will not sink in the sands of 
oblivion. The bullets of our strugglers are the imminent 
response to the Zionists. Violent confrontations with the 
occupiers are the road that our people have willingly pursued. 
Our people will not abandon their sincere option until the 
entire sacred Palestinian homeland is liberated and until we 
avenge every Palestinian soul killed by the filthy Zionist hands. 

</TEXT>

